title: Chris Cagle - My Life's Been A Country Song
description:
I have always loved Chris Cagle&#039;s music and this new album is no exception! There is great mixture of high-energy songs that are even better when seen live and slower songs that are full of the geniune emotion that he always conveys. All in all a great well-rounded album! Go see him in concert and you will love the songs even more!
